Description: Package containing a pinyin drilling executable Rscript in the package exec directory.
  Also contains Pinyin to IPA and Zhuyin functions.
Depends: dplyr, stringr, optparse, scales
SystemDepends: cjklib i.e. ``sudo -H pip install cjklib``
